check_mk Plugin to check sms deamon smsd.

The client plugin will check the status of smsd from Keijo Kasvi.
Please configure your smsd to output the smsd status monitor file
http://smstools3.kekekasvi.com/index.php?p=statusmonitor

Change the location of status file in agentfile.

The check was tested on the following Linux versions: Debian Squeeze

Any feedback welcome, PM to karsten.schoeke[at]geobasis-bb[dot]de. 
I'm also reading the german check_mk ML: checkmk-de@lists.mathias-kettner.de

INSTALLATION INSTRUCTIONS

On your check_mk clients:
Install the the check_mk agent plugin under /usr/lib/check_mk/plugins/

On your check server:

Install the smsd-x.x.mk package.
